Makeflags:
  EXECUTE_IN_RAM
    Place the app in RAM instead of in flash.

  CONFIG_NRF52_TEST_RADIO
    Enables a processor specific module for testing the radio.
    See test-radio/.

  CONFIG_NRF52_TEST_BLE_DTM
    Enables a processor specific module for testing the radio in a BLE manner.
    See test-ble-dtm/.

  CONFIG_GPIO_IRQ
    Enables gpio irq callback functionality.

See nrf-flash.mk for convenience targets for flashing, debugging etc.
